					<description><![CDATA[<p>Nas.com, an AI-enabled digital business platform launched by creator Nuseir Yassin, who is also the creator of the &#8220;Nas Daily&#8221; brand with 70 million followers, announced the closing of a</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/nas-com-secures-27m-for-ai-creator-economy-growth/" data-wpel-link="internal">Nas.Com Secures $27M for AI Creator Economy Growth</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><a href="http://nas.com" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener external noreferrer" data-wpel-link="external"><span style="font-weight: 400">Nas.com</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400">, an AI-enabled digital business platform launched by creator Nuseir Yassin, who is also the creator of the &#8220;Nas Daily&#8221; brand with 70 million followers, announced the closing of a $27m series A </span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/zum-raises-100m-to-expand-connected-mobility-platform/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noopener" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400">funding </span></a><span style="font-weight: 400">round. </span>Led by Khosla Ventures, the funding will help it become part of the evolution of the &#8220;solo economy&#8221;. Attending the round were 500 global and strategic investors: Shuo Wang, Stanley Tang, Scott Adelson, and Tim Ferriss.</p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400">Bridging the Gap for the &#8220;Solo Entrepreneur&#8221;</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">The traditional creative economy has reached its peak with the top 3%. It is now expanding to the remaining 97% with Nas.com, the &#8220;solo entrepreneurs&#8221;. The opening of over 532,000 business applications in the United States in January 2066 by the U.S. Census Bureau demonstrates a significant, moving trend of independent one-man businesses.</span></p>
<div id="attachment_200116" style="width: 410px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><img decoding="async" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-200116" class="wp-image-200116" src="https://ventureburn.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/04/Nas.com_.jpeg" alt="Nas.com logo" width="400" height="400" /><p id="caption-attachment-200116" class="wp-caption-text">Source: Nas.com</p></div>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">You may find that forums exist for those wanting to sell a product; a &#8220;business name generator&#8221; is great, and an easy-to-use publishing platform is available. However, where do you go when you want to find your first customers?</span></p>
<p>“In the announcement, Nuseir Yassin said the creator economy was built for the 3%.” The solo economy serves everyone else. “AI is destroying jobs, but it also just gave every person on earth a way to replace their boss, not let bosses replace them.”</p>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">More News:</span><a href="https://ventureburn.com/zum-raises-100m-to-expand-connected-mobility-platform/" data-wpel-link="internal"><span style="font-weight: 400"> Zum Raises $100M to Expand Connected Mobility Platform</span></a></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400">A Full-Stack AI Solution</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Nas.com makes business easy: a full-fledged, AI-powered business builder. Makes it easy for anyone without any tech, marketing or design background to go from an idea to a business that generates revenue. Features of the platform are:</span></p>
<ul>
<li style="font-weight: 400"><b>AI-Driven Creation</b><span style="font-weight: 400">: Point your phone at a product or concept, and the AI creates the digital/physical products along with shopfront design.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400"><b>Marketing Automation</b><span style="font-weight: 400">: It automatically generates marketing copy, creates advertising campaigns, and manages customer acquisition.</span></li>
<li style="font-weight: 400"><b>Operations</b><span style="font-weight: 400">: It has features for community management, memberships, and effortless global payments and shipping.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">Again, the model has proved itself, as in 2025 the company grew revenue 5x. The site, which currently has 3.5 million members in over 150 countries, has 20,000 paying business owners, of which over 90% are individual operators.</span></p>
<h2><span style="font-weight: 400">Future Growth and Expansion</span></h2>
<p><span style="font-weight: 400">New capital will be targeted at a three-way growth plan. </span>Growing engineering headcount so that AI products can be made faster, building out a corporate team, and aggressively pushing international expansion. &#8220;The next wave of wealth will not come exclusively from the Fortune 500, but from hundreds of millions of people.&#8221;</p>
<p>The post <a href="https://ventureburn.com/nas-com-secures-27m-for-ai-creator-economy-growth/" data-wpel-link="internal">Nas.Com Secures $27M for AI Creator Economy Growth</a> appeared first on <a href="https://ventureburn.com" data-wpel-link="internal">Ventureburn</a>.</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
		
		
